	<h1 class="title">这些新色情杂志，你就不必把它们藏在床垫下了</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
				<span class="name">Ravi Somaiya</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-01-22 09:39:22 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/5428/medium/5428.JPG?1436687259" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


